Name: Note
Desc_: Data is updated daily by about 4 p.m. and includes cases reported through the previous day.

Name: Note
Desc_: The number of cases includes people who have had a test that indicated they were positive for COVID-19. The number of cases also includes epidemiologically-linked cases -- or cases where public health epidemiologists have determined that infection is high

Name: Note
Desc_: Total people tested may not include all negative results. Testing data excludes serology and only counts PCR.
